\mu_{n,n}
\mu_{n,i}=\frac{i!}{n^{i}}\times\sum_{j=0}^{i}\frac{n^{j}}{j!}
\mu_{n,n}=\frac{n!}{n^{n}}\times\sum_{j=0}^{n}\frac{n^{j}}{j!}
